.DT
npc_unhear_shouts
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
npc_unhear_shouts

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
npc_unhear_shouts -  Removes an NPC from the list of NPC's who are to receive shout events.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int npc_unhear_shouts(object oldlistener)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^oldlistener%^RESET%^ - NPC object to be removed from the list
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successfully removed

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/broadcaster.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Removes an NPC from the list of NPC's who are to receive shout events.
The NPC need not be removed from this list when he dies -- desting
the NPC object has the same effect as calling npc_unhear_shouts().

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/global/events->event_person_shout(), npc_hear_shouts()

.EP

